title: John Burnet of Barns: A Romance
author: Buchan, John
snippet: Midday found me in the nick of the hill above Glencotho debating on myafter course.

title: John Burnet of Barns: A Romance
author: Buchan, John
snippet: There were the Tweedies ofQuarter and Glencotho, kin to myself on the mother's side, not to speakof a score of herds whom I had dealings with.
